	<h1 class="title">这家美术馆想展示表演艺术，他们请来了一支怪乐队 | 100 个有想法的人</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/43366/small/43366.jpg?1430896699" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">王民超 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-02-20 12:51:14 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
